<p>I'm attempting to present a <code>UIViewController</code> when a cell is selected in a <code>UITableView</code>.  The problem is that the <code>UIViewController</code>'s <code>UITableView</code> and <code>UIButton</code> do not display when the modal presentations style is set to Form Sheet, but they do work when the presentation style is set to Page Sheet. </p>  <p>Below is the code I am using to present the <code>UIViewController</code>.  And screenshots for some of the settings in the storyboard.  The screenshot of the simulator shows that the <code>UIView</code> in the <code>UIViewController</code> is the only thing displayed when Form Sheet is used.</p>  <pre><code>var vc = self.storyboard?.instantiateViewControllerWithIdentifier("SeasonsSetting") as! SeasonsSettingViewController self.navigationController?.presentViewController(vc, animated: true, completion: nil) </code></pre>  <p><a href="http://i.stack.imgur.com/Vg2xg.png" rel="nofollow"><img src="http://i.stack.imgur.com/Vg2xg.png" alt="enter image description here"></a></p>  <p><a href="http://i.stack.imgur.com/MdCJz.png" rel="nofollow"><img src="http://i.stack.imgur.com/MdCJz.png" alt="enter image description here"></a></p>  <p><a href="http://i.stack.imgur.com/ehzWL.png" rel="nofollow"><img src="http://i.stack.imgur.com/ehzWL.png" alt="enter image description here"></a></p>